geekast is a nodecast's client 

INSTALL

install libsigar if not packaged in your linux distribution :

cp src/externals/hyperic-sigar-1.6.4/sigar-bin/lib/libsigar-amd64-linux.so /usr/local/lib/libsigar.so
cp src/externals/hyperic-sigar-1.6.4/sigar-bin/include/* /usr/local/include/

qmake
make

USAGE :
server : http://api.nodecast.net
email : your nodecast's email
API key : the private key is in your preferences on the nodecast.net website
private host UUID : nodecast generate this key when geekast push datas for the first time.

DO NOT PUBLISH the API key and the private host UUID.


contact : fredix at nodecast dot net
